<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Copenhagen_interpretation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>G. Weihs et al., Phys. Rev. Lett. 81 (1998) 5039</li>
<li>M. Rowe et al., Nature 409 (2001) 791.</li>
<li>J.A. Wheeler &amp; W.H. Zurek (eds) , Quantum Theory and Measurement, Princeton University Press 1983</li>
<li>A. Petersen, Quantum Physics and the Philosophical Tradition, MIT Press 1968</li>
<li>H. Margeneau, The Nature of Physical Reality, McGraw-Hill 1950</li>
<li>M. Chown, Forever Quantum, New Scientist No. 2595 (2007) 37.</li>
<li>T. Schürmann, A Single Particle Uncertainty Relation, Acta Physica Polonica B39 (2008) 587. <a href="http://th-www.if.uj.edu.pl/acta/vol39/pdf/v39p0587.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://th-www.if.uj.edu.pl/acta/vol39/pdf/v39p0587.pdf" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
</ul>
